{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/documentation\/ViewEnvironmentUI\/UIKit\/UIViewController\/environment"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironment"},{"type":"text","text":" that is flowing through the propagation hierarchy."}],"metadata":{"title":"environment","modules":[{"name":"ViewEnvironmentUI"}],"externalID":"s:17ViewEnvironmentUI0aB11PropagatingPAAE11environment0aB0AEVvp::SYNTHESIZED::c:objc(cs)UIViewController","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"ViewEnvironmentUI","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"environment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ViewEnvironment","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"environment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ViewEnvironment","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to provide overrides for the environment as it flows through a node, you should conform to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and provide those overrides in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"customize(environment:)"},{"type":"text","text":". E.g.:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["func customize(environment: inout ViewEnvironment) {","    environment.traits.mode = .dark","}"],"syntax":"sw